'''亞莉特克拉·布魯'''（{{lang-en|Alektra Blue}}，{{bd|1983年|6月9日||}}）是名[[美國|美國]][[色情演員|色情演員]]。

布魯出生於[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]][[鳳凰城|鳳凰城]]，成長於[[德克薩斯州|德州]][[達拉斯|達拉斯]]。<ref name=XCitement/> 她在2005年1月進入成人業界。<ref name="XCitement">{{Cite web | url=http://www.xcitement.com/interview/?page_id=445 | title=Xcitement Interviews - Alektra Blue and Mikayla Mendez | accessdate=2008-10-21 | author=Cindi Loftus | publisher=Xcitement.com | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081005034205/http://www.xcitement.com/interview/?page_id=445 | archivedate=2008-10-05 }}</ref> 帶她進入業界的是她好友[[塔琳·湯瑪斯|塔琳·湯瑪斯]]（Taryn Thomas）。布魯現任丈夫是成人男星與導演{{tsl|en|Pat Myne|}}。<ref name="xrent">{{cite web|url=http://www.xrentdvd.com/Porn_Star_Interviews/Alektra_Blue.html|title=Inside Alektra Blue|accessdate=2007-12-17|author=Big D|date=2006-11-13|publisher=XRentDVD|archive-date=2015-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228114515/http://www.xrentdvd.com/Porn_Star_Interviews/Alektra_Blue.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年4月，布魯成為《[[閣樓_(雜誌)|閣樓]]》當月閣樓寵物<ref name=penthouseMySpace>{{cite web|url=http://www.myspace.com/penthouse|title=Penthouse Magazine's Official MySpace Page|publisher=penthouse.com|accessdate=2011-05-08|archive-date=2012-07-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68sJfwknc?url=http://www.myspace.com/penthouse|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=PenthouseMagazine>{{cite web|url=http://www.penthousemagazine.com|title=Penthouse Magazine|accessdate=2020-09-29|archive-date=2015-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150511164937/http://penthousemagazine.com/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並與[[邪惡影像|邪惡影像]]簽下專屬合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.avn.com/performer/articles/29987.html|title=Wicked Pictures Signs Alektra Blue, Mikayla Mendez|author=David Sullivan|date=2008-05-02|publisher=avn.com|accessdate=2011-05-08|archive-date=2008-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202174820/http://www.avn.com/performer/articles/29987.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

布魯曾客串[[女神卡卡|女神卡卡]]與[[碧昂絲|碧昂絲]]在2010年合作的《Telephone》音樂錄影帶。<ref name=telephone>{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/37556.html|title=jessica drake, Alektra Blue Imprison Lady Gaga and Beyonce|accessdate=2010-03-23|date=2010-03-12|publisher=AVN.com|archive-date=2010-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100322194408/http://business.avn.com/articles/37556.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 她也與[[邪惡影像|邪惡影像]]專屬女星[[凱拉妮·雷|凱拉妮·雷]]（Kaylani Lei）一同出席2010年4月的[[言論自由聯盟|言論自由聯盟]]（Free Speech Coalition）「All-Star Anti-Piracy PSA」活動。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4xNzsTHA1nI |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-05-08 |archive-date=2010-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100520093712/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4xNzsTHA1nI |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://aipdaily.com/2010/wickeds-kaylani-lei-and-alektra-blue-appear-in-fsc-anti-piracy-video/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-11-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140830224119/http://aipdaily.com/2010/wickeds-kaylani-lei-and-alektra-blue-appear-in-fsc-anti-piracy-video/ |archivedate=2014-08-30 }}</ref>

